            "title": "The forest holds the knowledge of our ancestors",
            "description": "At Shell, we embedded a commitment to contribute to sustainable development into our strategy. What does that mean in practice?"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "story_card",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What does it take to design a vast and complex offshore oil and gas facility?",
            "description": "How innovation, resilience, and collaboration fuelled a deep-water comeback for Gato do Mato in Brazil."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "story_card",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Platforms for change",
            "description": "Marking International Women's Day, the first woman to work offshore for Shell in the USA, along with two of the most recent, share their experiences of life at sea."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "story_card",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Penguins: Next generation platform starts production in the UK North Sea",
            "description": "More compact and efficient than its predecessor, Penguins will deliver secure energy from one of the North Sea's most iconic oil and gas fields."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "story_card",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Getting more out of a Norwegian gas field",
            "description": "A pioneering project is set to increase the amount of gas recovered from a field which supplies energy across Europe."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "story_card",
          "settings": {
            "title": "A sea change for oil and gas workers",
            "description": "As the global energy transition gathers pace, oil and gas workers are discovering their skills and expertise are in high demand for the future."
          }
        },
        {
